    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "yeah, i checked the receiving logs and they seem mostly okay. it doesn't look like a massive intake error. but it is weird because it's always just a few units, nothing big enough to trigger a major investigation. \n\nit's almost like they're just... vanishing. do you think there's anything else it could be? like maybe something with the scanning process or how units are packed?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
