      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "\"Vanishing\" units, when they are small and consistent, often point to systemic procedural issues rather than one big mistake. It's very possible that the scanning process is missing some items, or perhaps they are being accidentally bundled or mislabeled during the picking or packing stage. You might want to review the workflow at the packing station with a focus on how units are physically verified before being moved to the final outbound staging area.",
