    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "we did check the packing station and the staff say everything looks fine on their end. no visible errors or skipped scans. but the numbers keep drifting down by those tiny amounts every single week.\n\nis there any chance it's a technical glitch in the database where it's just dropping entries, or is it more likely something physical? it feels so random.",
